The license finder only works with licenses starting with THR.

*) Please work with filters: Unresolved + yet_to_review + rental = self_contained + hoe_violation = true.

*) The client is only interested in whole houses and apartments (not interested in rooms or ADUs).

*) To use GIS optimally, activate the following: Land Management - Property and Planning. Select the following options:

*) Land Divisions: Divides the parcels.

*) Parcel Cadastre: Shows the APNs.

*) Valuation Cadastre: Shows the Land Use and Property Address.

*) There are no public records, as privacy laws in the country protect property data.

*) Some addresses don’t have the Zip Code, in these cases, it's mandatory to perform AO.

*) This is an example of an address in Adelaide: Floor 16 1701/10 Balfours Way, Adelaide, SA 5000. The floor is determined by the unit number. In this case, the unit is 1701, which means it is on the 17th floor.

When mapping 6235 E Thunderbird Rd, Scottsdale, AZ 85254, be careful about the structure: If they rent everything all together is the main structure; if they rent the Guest Suites and Suite B is the main structure + NSC, if they rent any of the other units is unit one of many (Refer to the photo down below).

Address Alert: Be cautious with the address 404 N Tarnava St, Port Isabel, TX 78578, as it consists of multiple apartments, each with a unique APN.

Properties in Harbor Town, Laguna Vista, TX 78578, and Monte Bonito, N Valencia do not require an Address Override (AO); they are accurate as reflected in the Cyborg data.

Cameron County Listings: Several property listings in Cameron County are located in Mexico. As a best practice, these should be marked in Cyborg as "The listing is outside of the current region" rather than "NMF". This ensures they won’t appear on Rentalscape or remain pending for review in FP, as they are unmappable listings.

South Padre Island Condos: For condos in South Padre Island, exercise caution since each unit has its own APN. Always utilize the Unit Box, even if Cyborg includes the unit in the address and Address Overrides for Units: If the Cyborg address does not include the unit, you must perform an Address Override to incorporate the unit and ensure it is also added to the Unit Box.
